            <title>1.3.4</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 11:29:36 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>65</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[- Fixed the menu bar icon disappearing. It could vanish (leaving no icon to click) when the Settings window opened — including automatically when an update was found. The menu bar icon now stays put.
- Removed the animation when the "Check for Updates" window grows from checking to showing the release details — it now switches instantly.
]]></description>
